snippet.title: A Stickman Reality
snippet.description:
Now available on Steam as free download:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/889220/A_Stickman_Reality/

This the trailer for ImproVive's VR experience "A Stickman Reality". 
In this experience you are in the middle of a story where stickmen invade your world.
Make contact with the stickman world. Find out what technology they are using. But be careful, few have returned to tell their tale.
